<p>For FreeSwitch deployment, please follow steps as below</p>
<p>
 <br>
</p>
<p>.1 Create a new VM&nbsp; ( droplet ) in the DO portal. The VM should be created separately from the DO managed Kubernetes cluster, as the kubernetes based deployments of the FreeSwitch are not yet available.&nbsp;</p>
<p>.2 Once the VM is ready, SSH into the IP address assigned to the VM and use the password that you provided during creation process of the VM (public key method is also available in case password is not used )</p>
<p>3. Follow the steps mentioned in <a href="https://docs.expertflow.com/x/pA1kD" data-scope="external" rel="external noreferrer">FreeSwitch deployment Guide</a></p>
